<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 15:11:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，布鲁塞尔可能重新考虑对大众、宝马的中国电动汽车进口关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</link><description>两位知情人士称，欧盟委员会已向大众汽车和宝马发出信号，可能会考虑降低这两家汽车制造商进口中国制造的电动汽车的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:48:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/brussels-may-rethink-china-ev-import-tariffs-volkswagen-bmw-sources-say-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>伊朗代理外长对恢复核协议谈判持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-open-resuming-nuclear-accord-talks-acting-foreign-minister-2024-07-16/</link><description>伊朗代理外交部长在周二发表的采访中告诉《新闻周刊》杂志，德黑兰仍然愿意与华盛顿恢复参与核协议的谈判。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 14:21:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-open-resuming-nuclear-accord-talks-acting-foreign-minister-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰在周一欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的投票中投了弃权票</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/finland-abstained-mondays-vote-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2024-07-16/</link><description>芬兰驻欧盟大使馆的一位官员周二表示，芬兰在周一欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车临时关税进行的投票中投了弃权票。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:33:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/finland-abstained-mondays-vote-eu-tariffs-china-evs-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织预计全球增长稳定，警告通货紧缩势头放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-sees-steady-global-growth-warns-slowing-disinflation-momentum-2024-07-16/</link><description>国际货币基金组织(IMF)周二表示，由于美国经济活动降温、欧洲触底反弹以及中国消费和出口走强，全球经济预计未来两年将温和增长，但这一道路上的风险比比皆是。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:08:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/imf-sees-steady-global-growth-warns-slowing-disinflation-momentum-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>贸易机构负责人表示，台湾企业将供应链从中国转移到印度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</link><description>台湾主要贸易机构负责人告诉路透社，随着主要经济体之间的全球贸易紧张局势加剧，台北和新德里加强了经济联系，台湾企业正在将供应链从中国转移到印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-firms-shift-supply-chains-india-china-trade-body-chief-says-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，普华永道考虑将中国金融服务审计人员减半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</link><description>两名知情人士表示，普华永道 (PwC) 正在考虑将其在中国的金融服务审计人员裁减至多一半，原因是监管调查和客户流失使业务前景黯淡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/pwc-weighs-halving-china-financial-services-audit-staff-say-sources-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔激发利率希望，特朗普贸易降温</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-16/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 10:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国国有券商将扩大在东南亚的投资银行业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</link><description>国有券商中国银河证券 (CGS) 的一名高级管理人员表示，计划明年将其在东南亚的投资银行团队从目前的 30 人扩大到 50 人，并押注在市场低迷的情况下该地区的交易量会增加在家里。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:09:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinese-state-owned-brokerage-ramp-up-investment-banking-business-southeast-asia-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行聘请前英国政治家领导新基础设施部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</link><description>一位高级银行高管告诉路透社，英国汇丰银行已成立一个新部门，以挖掘与世界向低碳经济转型相关的基础设施融资和项目融资交易，并聘请了一位前英国政治家来领导该部门。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/hsbc-launches-new-climate-focused-infrastructure-finance-unit-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>鉴于“致命四方”的威胁，英国将增强武装力量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</link><description>英国表示，将加强其“空心化”的武装部队，以确保该国做好准备面对由中国、伊朗、朝鲜和俄罗斯组成的防务审查负责人所说的“致命四方”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:49:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-boost-armed-forces-given-threat-deadly-quartet-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚 ADE 预计新飞机短缺导致飞机维修激增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</link><description>马来西亚航空服务公司亚洲数字工程 (ADE) 首席执行官马赫什·库马尔 (Mahesh Kumar) 表示，由于新飞机短缺，航空公司将延长飞机的飞行时间，全球飞机维修行业将在未来六年出现更大增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 07:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/malaysias-ade-sees-boom-aircraft-repairs-amid-new-plane-shortages-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>美银表示，投资者持乐观态度，但对地缘政治持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</link><description>美国银行周二的全球基金经理调查显示，对美国利率将下降、防止经济硬着陆的预期使投资者保持看涨情绪，尽管地缘政治构成了这种情况的最大风险。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:53:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/investors-stay-bullish-july-fuelled-by-fed-rate-outlook-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>对于全球投资者来说，中国是一个缓慢燃烧的贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</link><description>对于在中国股市持有资金的全球投资者来说，最新的经济数据并没有带来任何安慰，只是提醒他们，他们所押注的复苏需要一段时间才能实现。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 06:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/global-investors-china-is-slow-burning-trade-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软损害了奢侈品公司历峰集团的销售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</link><description>卡地亚母公司历峰集团周二表示，截至 6 月份的三个月内，该奢侈品集团的销售额几乎持平，中国需求下滑导致整体业绩略低于预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-says-quarterly-sales-up-1-constant-exchange-rates-2024-07-16/</guid></item><item><title>ASML订单量预计将因AI芯片热潮而猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</link><description>计算机芯片制造商的顶级设备供应商 ASML 预计将在其新老板周三公布第二季度业绩时报告新订单大量涌入，因为客户扩大产能以满足人工智能芯片蓬勃发展的需求。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 05:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmls-order-book-expected-benefit-ai-chip-boom-2024-07-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>